For DM performance measurement:

    1. Change all the "LDB_PP*_HCW_DELAY" to 1 in opt file
    2. Run following tests lists for performance measurement:
        a. dm_perf_short.list       ==> default HCW traffic
        b. dm_perf_short_1k.list    ==> 1K HCWs per PP
        c. dm_perf_short_5k.list    ==> 5K HCWs per PP
    3. Use following script to generate stats:
        verif/tb/hqm/tests/hcw_perf_dm_test1/genrpt.pl
